Using Linux screen command

	- This is for running a command that will run for a long time

ex. ping google.com gor a long time

#screen (press enter)

run command

now press ctrl + a
 now press ctrl + d

Now when you are ready to pull up the already running session type scree -dr
*detaches any current sessions and the r attaches the old session

once you are done with the project exit will quit all screen sessions and get back to the normal terminal
